1
00:01:37,333 --> 00:01:41,250
[groaning]

2
00:01:42,791 --> 00:01:46,875
Mugen. Bring forth calamity!

3
00:01:48,916 --> 00:01:51,083
Now, Nigen Swords!

4
00:01:53,833 --> 00:01:55,416
[LAVI]
Be careful, Yu!

5
00:01:55,500 --> 00:01:58,416
That thing's ridiculously
hard to...

6
00:01:58,500 --> 00:02:01,000
[HUGE AKUMA B screams]

7
00:02:02,875 --> 00:02:05,125
...kill...

8
00:02:11,333 --> 00:02:12,833
Lavi. Listen.

9
00:02:12,916 --> 00:02:14,291
[LAVI]
Y-Yeah?

10
00:02:14,375 --> 00:02:17,666
If I ever hear you refer to
me by my first name again,

11
00:02:17,750 --> 00:02:19,708
you're a dead man.

12
00:02:19,791 --> 00:02:22,666
[LAVI]
You're as scary as ever.

13
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:30,458
[MILLENNIUM EARL]
Such impudence!

14
00:02:34,291 --> 00:02:36,250
That must be...

15
00:02:36,333 --> 00:02:37,916
[gasps]

16
00:02:55,083 --> 00:02:56,333
What is that?

17
00:02:56,416 --> 00:02:58,375
Look out!

18
00:02:59,958 --> 00:03:01,583
[KRORY, BOOKMAN grunt]

19
00:03:09,750 --> 00:03:10,916
Miranda!

20
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,458
Please, speak to me!

21
00:03:12,541 --> 00:03:14,583
Come on... Wake up!

22
00:03:14,666 --> 00:03:15,958
[MIRANDA groaning]

23
00:03:16,041 --> 00:03:18,416
[CHAOZII]
No, it's too late!

24
00:03:36,208 --> 00:03:38,041
[KANDA grunts]

25
00:03:55,541 --> 00:03:57,791
[KANDA grunting]

26
00:04:11,125 --> 00:04:13,041
[LENALEE gasps]
Lavi!

27
00:04:13,125 --> 00:04:14,500
[LAVI]
Uh!

28
00:04:20,875 --> 00:04:22,583
Well, that was scary!

29
00:04:22,666 --> 00:04:25,833
Lenalee, are you okay out there?

30
00:04:25,916 --> 00:04:28,041
[LENALEE]
I'm sorry.

31
00:04:28,125 --> 00:04:31,041
You're always saving me.

32
00:04:33,250 --> 00:04:35,291
That's not the Lenalee I know.

33
00:04:35,375 --> 00:04:37,208
Let's win this
and go home, okay?

34
00:04:37,291 --> 00:04:39,541
[LENALEE]
Huh?

35
00:04:39,625 --> 00:04:41,000
Mm!

36
00:04:41,083 --> 00:04:42,916
[LAVI]
Here. This way.

37
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:46,000
[BOTH grunting]

38
00:04:47,750 --> 00:04:49,458
[LAVI gasps]

39
00:04:52,250 --> 00:04:55,833
[LAVI]
Lenalee!

40
00:05:00,291 --> 00:05:03,250
Time to disappear.

41
00:05:56,791 --> 00:05:58,875
My!

42
00:05:58,958 --> 00:06:01,916
You are nothing if not
thorough, Lord Millennium.

43
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:04,291
I'm rather impressed!

44
00:06:04,375 --> 00:06:07,791
Edo is completely annihilated.

45
00:06:12,375 --> 00:06:15,083
[MILLENNIUM EARL sneezes]

46
00:06:15,166 --> 00:06:16,000
[SKINN]
Huh...?

47
00:06:16,083 --> 00:06:18,041
Uh...

48
00:06:18,125 --> 00:06:22,291
[MILLENNIUM EARL sneezing]

49
00:06:22,375 --> 00:06:25,166
[LERO] Are you all right,
Lord Millennium, Lero?

50
00:06:25,250 --> 00:06:27,291
Oops, your nose
is running, Lero!

51
00:06:27,375 --> 00:06:28,500
[MILLENNIUM EARL coughs]

52
00:06:28,583 --> 00:06:31,375
[TYKI] Oh. I've got eyes
on an Exorcist here.

53
00:06:31,458 --> 00:06:34,708
And he's still in one piece.

54
00:06:34,791 --> 00:06:39,125
[KANDA grunting]
Damn you...

55
00:06:40,416 --> 00:06:43,583
You won't defeat me. Bastards!

56
00:06:44,750 --> 00:06:45,625
[TIEDOLL]
Marie.

57
00:06:45,708 --> 00:06:47,458
Can you hear me?

58
00:06:47,541 --> 00:06:50,041
[MARIE]
Y... Yes, Master.

59
00:06:50,125 --> 00:06:51,791
[TIEDOLL]
Are you injured?

60
00:06:51,875 --> 00:06:54,416
[MARIE]
I'll... I'll be all right.

61
00:06:54,500 --> 00:06:56,750
What on earth was that?

62
00:06:56,833 --> 00:06:59,083
[TIEDOLL] It must have been
the Earl's special ability.

63
00:06:59,166 --> 00:07:02,791
It's nothing short of a genuine
miracle that you all survived.

64
00:07:02,875 --> 00:07:04,583
[MARIE grunts]

65
00:07:04,666 --> 00:07:06,708
[TIEDOLL] Can you check
on the others for me?

66
00:07:06,791 --> 00:07:08,666
Yes, sir.

67
00:07:09,916 --> 00:07:15,166
No. The Cross Unit's heartbeats
are even fainter than ours are.

68
00:07:15,250 --> 00:07:19,250
And some of them are
barely managing to hold on.

69
00:07:21,750 --> 00:07:25,333
[LENALEE]
Every...one...

70
00:07:28,250 --> 00:07:30,375
[LENALEE]
Please...

71
00:07:33,666 --> 00:07:37,500
That was insane. What happened?

72
00:07:37,583 --> 00:07:38,458
[gasps]

73
00:07:38,541 --> 00:07:41,208
[MIRANDA whimpering]

74
00:07:44,083 --> 00:07:45,875
Wait, Exorcist Miranda!

75
00:07:45,958 --> 00:07:49,666
No way! Did you use
your power to protect us?

76
00:07:49,750 --> 00:07:51,833
I can fix what's broken,

77
00:07:51,916 --> 00:07:55,166
but my clock can't do
anything for the dead.

78
00:07:55,250 --> 00:07:56,625
[CHAOZII gasps]

79
00:07:56,708 --> 00:07:58,375
And I...

80
00:07:58,458 --> 00:08:02,291
I wasn't quick enough
to bring everyone back.

81
00:08:05,791 --> 00:08:08,000
[LENALEE]
Miranda...

82
00:08:16,291 --> 00:08:18,375
[LAVI groans]

83
00:08:21,541 --> 00:08:23,541
Hold on, Lenalee.

84
00:08:23,625 --> 00:08:27,708
[LAVI groaning]

85
00:08:27,791 --> 00:08:29,250
[LAVI]
Damn!

86
00:08:29,333 --> 00:08:32,958
[LAVI grunting]

87
00:08:33,041 --> 00:08:34,000
[LENALEE]
Lavi.

88
00:08:34,083 --> 00:08:35,375
[LAVI]
Uh?

89
00:08:42,875 --> 00:08:44,416
[LAVI gasps]

90
00:08:46,458 --> 00:08:48,708
[LAVI gasping]

91
00:09:00,041 --> 00:09:02,375
Again?

92
00:09:02,458 --> 00:09:06,458
[KANDA]
Hey. What is that?

93
00:09:06,541 --> 00:09:07,708
What's going on?

94
00:09:07,791 --> 00:09:08,750
[LENALEE]
Kanda.

95
00:09:08,833 --> 00:09:09,416
[gasps]

96
00:09:09,500 --> 00:09:10,333
[LENALEE]
Lavi.

97
00:09:10,416 --> 00:09:11,291
[LAVI gasps]

98
00:09:11,375 --> 00:09:12,958
[KANDA grunts]

99
00:09:13,041 --> 00:09:15,583
[LENALEE]
Everyone...

100
00:09:15,666 --> 00:09:18,583
Is that... really?

101
00:09:18,666 --> 00:09:20,875
It's Lenalee.

102
00:09:23,458 --> 00:09:27,125
[LENALEE]
You guys. I'm here!

103
00:09:27,208 --> 00:09:31,416
[MARIE] Hm? Is that
really Lenalee's voice?

104
00:09:31,500 --> 00:09:35,416
I've never heard anything
like it before.

105
00:09:35,500 --> 00:09:37,708
Oh, Lenalee.

106
00:09:37,791 --> 00:09:42,125
[TIEDOLL]
Hm? That voice is...

107
00:09:42,750 --> 00:09:43,875
What was that?

108
00:09:43,958 --> 00:09:45,416
So you heard it, too?

109
00:09:45,500 --> 00:09:46,791
[SKINN]
Yeah.

110
00:09:46,875 --> 00:09:49,833
[MILLENNIUM EARL]
How truly bizarre.

111
00:09:49,916 --> 00:09:50,791
[TYKI]
Yeah?

112
00:09:50,875 --> 00:09:53,250
What's that?

113
00:09:54,541 --> 00:09:55,541
[MILLENNIUM EARL]
Who'd have thought

114
00:09:55,625 --> 00:09:58,333
such a thing would ever
possibly happen?

115
00:09:58,416 --> 00:10:03,291
Heh. This is most unusual.

116
00:10:03,375 --> 00:10:04,750
[KANDA]
You're saying the Innocence

117
00:10:04,833 --> 00:10:08,125
decided to protect Lenalee's
life of its own free will?

118
00:10:08,208 --> 00:10:10,875
[LAVI]
Yeah.

119
00:10:10,958 --> 00:10:13,583
But she has an
Equipment Type Innocence.

120
00:10:13,666 --> 00:10:15,875
It can't!

121
00:10:15,958 --> 00:10:18,916
Most of them can't.
But this one...

122
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:22,541
Well, it seems to
be a special kind.

123
00:10:22,625 --> 00:10:25,166
A special kind?

124
00:10:25,250 --> 00:10:25,916
[gasps]

125
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,500
Don't tell me!

126
00:10:27,583 --> 00:10:29,208
Is this...?

127
00:10:31,083 --> 00:10:33,458
[LENALEE]
Everyone!

128
00:10:35,833 --> 00:10:37,208
[BOOKMAN]
Come to think of it,

129
00:10:37,291 --> 00:10:40,208
Miss Lena's Innocence has
voluntarily changed its form

130
00:10:40,291 --> 00:10:43,625
once before in order to
save its owner from dying.

131
00:10:43,708 --> 00:10:46,791
The fact that such a phenomenon
is occurring a second time

132
00:10:46,875 --> 00:10:48,416
could be a sign that...

133
00:10:48,500 --> 00:10:52,041
[TIEDOLL] If this is true, then
the Innocence Lenalee possesses

134
00:10:52,125 --> 00:10:57,000
is of a rare variety that's
extremely valuable to our team.

135
00:10:57,083 --> 00:11:00,541
And to the Millennium Earl.

136
00:11:07,166 --> 00:11:10,083
[MARIE]
What a sound.

137
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:12,625
[TIEDOLL]
Careful, Marie!

138
00:11:12,708 --> 00:11:14,875
The Earl has his eye on Lenalee!

139
00:11:14,958 --> 00:11:16,166
[MARIE gasps]

140
00:11:21,083 --> 00:11:22,333
Look above you!

141
00:11:22,416 --> 00:11:23,833
Kanda! Lavi!

142
00:11:23,916 --> 00:11:25,166
[gasps]

143
00:11:39,291 --> 00:11:40,833
Whoa!

144
00:11:40,916 --> 00:11:43,083
That really the best you can do?

145
00:11:43,166 --> 00:11:45,208
You're not half bad.

146
00:11:45,291 --> 00:11:48,666
Sorry, but the girl is mine!

147
00:11:48,750 --> 00:11:49,458
[gasps]

148
00:11:49,541 --> 00:11:51,000
[KANDA growls]

149
00:11:52,208 --> 00:11:53,916
[LAVI]
Yu!

150
00:12:01,083 --> 00:12:03,291
[yells]

151
00:12:05,250 --> 00:12:06,708
[KANDA grunts]

152
00:12:09,791 --> 00:12:10,958
Uh-oh.

153
00:12:11,041 --> 00:12:14,333
Now you can't swing that
flashy sword anymore.

154
00:12:15,416 --> 00:12:16,708
[TYKI]
My apologies.

155
00:12:16,791 --> 00:12:19,166
As much as I'd like to keep
having fun with you,

156
00:12:19,250 --> 00:12:21,791
the circumstances
won't allow it.

157
00:12:22,541 --> 00:12:25,000
It's the end of the
world as you know it.

158
00:12:25,083 --> 00:12:26,875
[KANDA gasps]

159
00:12:26,958 --> 00:12:29,750
[TYKI]
I can't wait to watch!

160
00:12:31,416 --> 00:12:33,166
[KANDA] You don't seem
to actually understand

161
00:12:33,250 --> 00:12:37,291
what's happening. You might
be the one who disappears.

162
00:12:37,375 --> 00:12:38,875
Huh?

163
00:12:43,541 --> 00:12:47,125
That expression. It's perfect.

164
00:12:48,333 --> 00:12:50,791
[TYKI]
This is your final moment.

165
00:12:50,875 --> 00:12:53,166
Take a good hard look!

166
00:12:57,416 --> 00:12:59,166
[TYKI gasps]

167
00:13:01,916 --> 00:13:02,791
Mugen.

168
00:13:02,875 --> 00:13:04,708
Nigen Swords!

169
00:13:07,916 --> 00:13:10,166
[TYKI]
Huh?

170
00:13:10,250 --> 00:13:12,416
Almost had me.

171
00:13:12,500 --> 00:13:13,916
[TYKI chuckles]

172
00:13:16,791 --> 00:13:19,166
Oh my, now it's
getting interesting!

173
00:13:19,250 --> 00:13:20,958
Shut up!

174
00:13:28,500 --> 00:13:32,166
You haven't changed
at all, have you?

175
00:13:32,250 --> 00:13:34,750
[LAVI gasping]

176
00:13:34,833 --> 00:13:38,458
Do you like sweets? 'Cause I do!

177
00:13:38,541 --> 00:13:40,041
[LENALEE]
Lavi!

178
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:45,458
[SKINN]
Huh? Hm?

179
00:13:45,541 --> 00:13:47,625
[LAVI yelling]

180
00:13:47,708 --> 00:13:49,041
[SKINN groans]

181
00:13:50,958 --> 00:13:52,541
I'll crush you!

182
00:13:52,625 --> 00:13:53,708
Grow...

183
00:13:53,791 --> 00:13:55,875
Grow.

184
00:13:55,958 --> 00:13:56,958
Grow!

185
00:13:57,041 --> 00:13:58,750
[SKINN groans]

186
00:14:03,708 --> 00:14:06,000
[SKINN]
Never, ever forgive!

187
00:14:09,791 --> 00:14:10,416
[LAVI gasps]

188
00:14:10,500 --> 00:14:13,750
[LAVI screams]

189
00:14:13,833 --> 00:14:17,666
[LAVI groaning]

190
00:14:23,208 --> 00:14:25,250
[LENALEE]
Lavi!

191
00:14:25,333 --> 00:14:27,333
No!

192
00:14:28,958 --> 00:14:30,791
[LAVI groans]

193
00:14:30,875 --> 00:14:33,791
[SKINN] Coming at me like that
after taking such a hard hit?

194
00:14:33,875 --> 00:14:35,916
You have got some
real nerve, buddy.

195
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:38,750
[gasping]

196
00:14:38,833 --> 00:14:40,500
And right when we
might've finally found

197
00:14:40,583 --> 00:14:42,500
just what we've
been looking for.

198
00:14:42,583 --> 00:14:44,500
Thanks for ruining the mood!

199
00:14:44,583 --> 00:14:46,333
[LAVI gasping]

200
00:14:46,416 --> 00:14:50,083
[LAVI] So, they really
are after Lenalee.

201
00:14:52,041 --> 00:14:53,625
[LAVI]
No.

202
00:14:54,375 --> 00:14:55,625
I mean.

203
00:14:55,708 --> 00:14:58,375
Am I still a part of this world?

204
00:14:58,458 --> 00:15:01,250
[LAVI gasping]
I can't give up.

205
00:15:01,333 --> 00:15:03,791
[SKINN]
Listen to me.

206
00:15:03,875 --> 00:15:06,375
I'll never forgive any of you.

207
00:15:06,458 --> 00:15:09,833
I won't forgive you damn
Exorcists, not ever!

208
00:15:09,916 --> 00:15:12,583
[LAVI groaning]

209
00:15:22,916 --> 00:15:24,791
[MARIE]
Lavi... Wake up!

210
00:15:24,875 --> 00:15:26,666
Lavi!

211
00:15:26,750 --> 00:15:29,958
[LAVI grunting]

212
00:15:31,333 --> 00:15:35,416
[SKINN groaning]

213
00:15:37,083 --> 00:15:38,375
Marie!

214
00:15:38,458 --> 00:15:41,333
[MARIE] I can only keep him
restrained for so long!

215
00:15:41,416 --> 00:15:44,708
Lavi, can you get on your feet?

216
00:15:44,791 --> 00:15:49,375
[LAVI grunts]

217
00:15:49,458 --> 00:15:53,208
[LAVI]
Yeah. I think I can handle it.

218
00:15:53,291 --> 00:15:58,500
Oh, you still want to fight
after the beating you just took?

219
00:15:58,583 --> 00:16:02,000
I don't care how many of you
damn Exorcists I'm up against,

220
00:16:02,083 --> 00:16:03,750
I'll still win.

221
00:16:03,833 --> 00:16:06,166
Don't be so sure.

222
00:16:11,833 --> 00:16:12,875
[LENALEE]
You guys!

223
00:16:12,958 --> 00:16:15,416
[MIRANDA gasps]
Lenalee!

224
00:16:15,500 --> 00:16:17,166
Hey, what's wrong, Miranda?

225
00:16:17,250 --> 00:16:19,708
Did you just hear something?

226
00:16:21,500 --> 00:16:22,958
Oh, no.

227
00:16:23,041 --> 00:16:25,708
It's nothing to worry about,
but still, thank you for asking.

228
00:16:25,791 --> 00:16:27,375
That's good to hear.

229
00:16:27,458 --> 00:16:29,250
You know, I never realized

230
00:16:29,333 --> 00:16:32,500
that Innocence was capable
of this kind of thing.

231
00:16:32,583 --> 00:16:33,833
I know it's temporary,

232
00:16:33,916 --> 00:16:36,000
but it's amazing that
you can heal their wounds.

233
00:16:36,083 --> 00:16:37,875
[MIRANDA] Well, if the
circumstances were different,

234
00:16:37,958 --> 00:16:40,333
I would prefer not
to use this ability.

235
00:16:40,416 --> 00:16:41,500
[CHAOZII]
Huh?

236
00:16:41,583 --> 00:16:42,583
[MIRANDA]
Even if they regain

237
00:16:42,666 --> 00:16:45,083
the strength to
fight temporarily,

238
00:16:45,166 --> 00:16:49,500
they're just going to keep
sustaining injuries.

239
00:16:49,583 --> 00:16:52,125
The longer it takes to bring
this battle to an end,

240
00:16:52,208 --> 00:16:54,166
the more likely
we'll lose someone.

241
00:16:54,250 --> 00:16:57,500
And then I won't be
able to revive them!

242
00:16:57,583 --> 00:17:01,500
I wish I were able to
help fight, but I...

243
00:17:01,583 --> 00:17:02,666
I can't!

244
00:17:02,750 --> 00:17:04,125
--[crash]
--[gasps]

245
00:17:04,208 --> 00:17:08,666
[HUGE AKUMA A roars]

246
00:17:17,833 --> 00:17:19,958
[CHAOZII] Looks like
the Akuma's on the move!

247
00:17:20,041 --> 00:17:21,958
Lenalee!

248
00:17:22,041 --> 00:17:25,416
[gasps] You must be...

249
00:17:25,500 --> 00:17:27,291
[TIEDOLL]
Mm.

250
00:17:31,500 --> 00:17:33,791
[TIEDOLL]
Don't move.

251
00:17:34,666 --> 00:17:38,375
O, Maker of Eden!

252
00:17:38,458 --> 00:17:40,500
Activate!

253
00:17:41,708 --> 00:17:44,750
And acknowledge the beauty
that's in the world!

254
00:17:44,833 --> 00:17:46,833
Art!

255
00:17:56,916 --> 00:18:02,750
[HUGE AKUMA A roars]

256
00:18:07,166 --> 00:18:09,541
[LAVI]
What just happened?

257
00:18:09,625 --> 00:18:11,458
[MARIE]
That's our Master's Innocence.

258
00:18:11,541 --> 00:18:14,166
I've never seen it in
that capacity though!

259
00:18:14,250 --> 00:18:15,708
[SKINN]
Heads up, punk!

260
00:18:15,791 --> 00:18:16,291
[MARIE groans]

261
00:18:16,375 --> 00:18:17,583
Marie!

262
00:18:17,666 --> 00:18:20,458
[SKINN laughs]

263
00:18:20,541 --> 00:18:23,500
Oh, I can't wait to
destroy all of you!

264
00:18:23,583 --> 00:18:26,500
It's gonna be so sweet!

265
00:18:27,750 --> 00:18:29,500
[TYKI]
You shouldn't be so stubborn.

266
00:18:29,583 --> 00:18:30,500
People hate that.

267
00:18:30,583 --> 00:18:32,291
[KANDA]
Shut up!

268
00:18:33,333 --> 00:18:36,916
[HUGE AKUMA A roars]

269
00:18:41,875 --> 00:18:43,375
[LENALEE]
Let me out!

270
00:18:43,458 --> 00:18:45,166
Lenalee!

271
00:18:47,625 --> 00:18:49,875
Oh, no.

272
00:18:49,958 --> 00:18:51,250
[LENALEE]
Please listen to me!

273
00:18:51,333 --> 00:18:54,291
