276
00:18:58,333 --> 00:18:59,875
[LENALEE gasps]

277
00:19:01,708 --> 00:19:03,250
[MILLENNIUM EARL grunts]

278
00:19:03,333 --> 00:19:04,041
[TIEDOLL grunts]

279
00:19:04,125 --> 00:19:05,041
[gasps]

280
00:19:05,125 --> 00:19:06,708
[LAVI gasps]

281
00:19:09,750 --> 00:19:11,666
You're wastin' your time.

282
00:19:11,750 --> 00:19:16,875
No matter how hard you try, your
power can never break into it.

283
00:19:16,958 --> 00:19:19,375
[KANDA grunting]

284
00:19:20,916 --> 00:19:23,958
