and made me angry.

285
00:19:29,458 --> 00:19:30,916
[LENALEE]
Uh!

286
00:19:36,083 --> 00:19:39,000
[EVIL SPIRITS laughing]

287
00:19:39,083 --> 00:19:40,916
[LENALEE whimpering]

288
00:19:43,458 --> 00:19:45,750
[LENALEE gasping]

289
00:19:45,833 --> 00:19:51,333
[MILLENNIUM EARL laughing]

290
00:19:53,416 --> 00:19:56,791
[LENALEE screams]

291
00:20:01,583 --> 00:20:03,416
[LENALEE]
Uh?

292
00:20:09,875 --> 00:20:11,458
[LENALEE gasps]

293
00:20:16,958 --> 00:20:19,250
What the...?

294
00:20:19,333 --> 00:20:23,541
Look at the sky. It split open.

295
00:20:30,750 --> 00:20:33,083
[MILLENNIUM EARL]
Why good evening.

296
00:20:33,916 --> 00:20:37,083
What a surprise
to see you again...

297
00:20:37,166 --> 00:20:39,041
...Allen Walker!

298
00:20:39,125 --> 00:20:41,916
[LENALEE gasping]

299
00:20:42,000 --> 00:20:44,000
[ALLEN]
Hmph.

300
00:20:44,083 --> 00:20:47,625
Hello, Earl. Good evening.

301
00:22:21,208 --> 00:22:22,916
[ALLEN]
My recently revived Innocence

302
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:24,916
enters a fierce one-on-one duel

303
00:22:25,000 --> 00:22:28,791
against the Millennium Earl
and his devastating weapon.

304
00:22:28,875 --> 00:22:32,375
