reaches a brand new stage.

305
00:22:32,458 --> 00:22:35,916
On the next <i>D.Gray-man</i> :
"Clown and Auguste."

306
00:22:36,000 --> 00:22:39,958
Bring forth salvation to
this poor Akuma's soul!

307
00:22:40,041 --> 00:22:42,083
You won't beat me. Never!

308
00:22:42,166 --> 00:22:44,375
Hey Kanda, your hair
keeps fallin' in your face.

309
00:22:44,458 --> 00:22:45,541
Maybe you should cut it?

310
00:22:45,625 --> 00:22:46,416
Shut up!

311
00:22:46,500 --> 00:22:47,916
Why don't you want to?

312
00:22:48,000 --> 00:22:49,875
None of your business, okay?

313
00:22:49,958 --> 00:22:52,166
Yeah, well, at least you
have long hair to cut.

314
00:22:52,250 --> 00:22:53,458
[KANDA]
Huh?

315
00:22:53,541 --> 00:22:56,750
[ALLEN] Great, you made
